          Hello Nour Shekho,
          Yes, these constructions are all grammatically correct and represent natural language use. However, I would say that the examples marked as more informal would not be appropriate in terms of style for the written part of the exam, so I would avoid these in that part. During the speaking part, however, as long as you use them correctly they are absolutely fine.
